Setup Instructions
==================

Server-side setup
----------------------------
1. Install NodeJS (http://nodejs.org/)
2. Install NodeJS dependencies

    npm install
    
3. Run the NodeJS application

    node app.js

Client-side setup
-----------------
1. Install bower (http://bower.io)
2. From the same folder that contains `bower.json`, run the following command to install any necessary JavaScript packages:

    bower install

Running the examples
--------------------
1. After running `node app.js`, visit `http://localhost:8888/index.html`
